<h1>BibleQL API Key Request Update</h1>

<p>Hi <%= @api_key_request.name %>,</p>

<p>Unfortunately, your API key request for the <strong><%= @api_key_request.environment %></strong> environment has been declined.</p>

<% if @api_key_request.rejection_reason.present? %>
  <p><strong>Reason:</strong> <%= @api_key_request.rejection_reason %></p>
<% end %>

<p>If you have questions, feel free to reach out or submit a new request.</p>
